同畢拉夫)換下新手角<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果係打覺醒料，可以去覺醒活動關打<br />\n<br />\n4. 升到D卡咁上下，請先去解超本氣果關，每日打潛力解放材料<br />\n(開放條件:<br />\nA. Rank 50以上<br />\nB.「超本気の超決戦」ステージ2.激突！超サイヤ人孫悟空のZ-HARD Clear)<br />\n<br />\n5. 3倍經驗完左可以去刷每日強襲角，知、速角優先，刷的意思係講每隻刷10隻刷到10技，再刷多隻5技放倉，準備以後解超強襲.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">角色代號</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>感謝 格劍巴整合代號名單</strong> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rncalhpj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frncalhpj&h=e1d19c4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>舊代號名單 感謝 photomore 巴打整合 </strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=09b39124\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">限定點心紙</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>感謝 願你今夜別離去巴打整合</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3a7jv78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3a7jv78.jpg&h=6489d757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">超激時間表</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>感謝 願你今夜別離去巴打整合</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gY57fC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgY57fC7.jpg&h=0b84a2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抽卡前請三思</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/032521_d685e